{"tid":436542,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"財經評論：養樓防老好過買股","createTime":"2017-10-15T08:40:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-15T20:38:34.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d711384a229922c7f2b8f042bee9d66a4aa0d72d","tid":436542,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T08:40:26.000Z","msg":"買樓等退休收租難？我話買股等退休更難，自訂甚麼藍籌組合，挑選不同板塊，睇市又睇勢，我睇，不如買樓更實際。<br />\n說辣招重稅、買第二套房要交重稅？早已被投資者借用阿仔阿女的首置客名義，一招搞碎。單身寡佬、無伴終老，或許高呼政府豁免長者買樓印花稅，但從政者不會看不到子女借父母名買樓的後果。15%稅很重？如何重，也不及子女長大成人養兒又養兩老那麼重。<br />\n睇過大埔太和中心、翠怡花園，以至沙田花園城的三百幾呎兩房租盤，不謀而合，業主都是七老八十的阿婆，早年買落用來退休收租。坦誠相對，婆婆早已供甩層樓，月月收一萬幾千，不用子女養自己。<br />\n近年百幾呎的劏房劣評如潮，但你有你鬧不人道，佢有佢收幾厘回報。剛入伙的尖沙嘴AVA62上月錄逾6宗租賃成交，月租1.2萬元至1.5萬元，扣除大嗱嗱每呎4.5元的管理費，回報率都貼近3厘，例如高層B室，實用面積206方呎，月租1.3萬元，2015年一手買入價498萬元，扣除每月927元管理費，回報率都有2.9厘。另一個中層A室，實用面積253平方呎，一房間隔，月租1.5萬元，2015年一手買入價502萬元，扣除每月1,138.5元，回報率去到3.3厘。<br />\n趁後生搵租客幫你供樓，等到廿幾年後，供滿會，月月收租來過活，日日飲茶刨波馬，得閒湊孫就樂滿家。<br />\n記者：陳家雄  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20171011/large/15386821.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171011%2Flarge%2F15386821.jpg&h=2054c2c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n趁後生搵租客幫你供樓，廿幾年後月月收租過活就最理想。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20171011/20179259\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F20171011%2F20179259&d=8igjPI8HX2AHJJWV7xU7oo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=23478ef1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F20171011%2F20179259&h=bcc60b78\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20171011/20179259</a>"},{"pid":"8385da17e67efdf4daee75fe9c22969421315903","tid":436542,"uid":22832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T08:42:11.000Z","msg":"樓有冇得一呎一呎咁買"},{"pid":"984430b6919e13a25aeebeeebf6b436ee9181a57","tid":436542,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T09:01:31.000Z","msg":"66以股代息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82015e9a12740960d9e244f97bdf0da9ca7c5f57","tid":436542,"uid":126329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T11:27:58.000Z","msg":"淨計防老收租 點樣同股票比"},{"pid":"21cd8b2a7d82770877c829de7bd8ed13c6bf47a4","tid":436542,"uid":47005,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T11:30:26.000Z","msg":"到老啦，終於供完啦，咪又係仲有筆維修費&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"c7af25e54954af9b3688cb08ee447182535af7a7","tid":436542,"uid":69506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T11:38:24.000Z","msg":"3釐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當你折舊1%，仲要裝修差餉維修。<br />\n隨時剩返一厘都冇。"},{"pid":"6840c78746bb927a8c99c2d6fd3b8f497f698c76","tid":436542,"uid":29608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T12:44:13.000Z","msg":"重點係capital gain <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ef4388c9351f888aa8be20eaed14e781da61551","tid":436542,"uid":18739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T20:38:34.000Z","msg":"傻閪，依家得3%回報先黎買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算俾你計埋槓桿效應倍大回報都係唔合理啦。"}]}